OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with showery
OL,6,Frain then becoming drier and brighter
OL,7,Flater this morning. A mainly dry
OL,8,Fafternoon with sunny intervals, the
OL,9,Fodd shower over Moray and north
OL,10,FAberdeenshire.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLate sunshine this evening
OL,13,Fbut quickly turning rather chilly. The
OL,14,Frest of the night will be dry and
OL,15,Flargely clear leading to a frost for
OL,16,Fmany.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FSome sunshine and a frost
OL,19,Ffirst thing in the morning for many.
OL,20,FThe rest of the day will then be dry,
OL,21,Fbright and partly cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
